eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* age 18-80 years old;
* newly diagnosed BC confirmed by biopsy or with BI-RADS category 4C or 5 lesions by US or MG;
* BC clinical stagecT1-3 cN0-3 M0;
* no prior treatment for BC.

Exclusion Criteria:

* pregnancy;
* breastfeeding;
* patients who were unwilling to undergo PET/CT scans.
